OL,5, Retail giant Amazon says it will pay   
OL,6, bonuses to attract temporary staff as  
OL,7, it recruits 20,000 seasonal UK workers.
OL,9,FThe company will offer the one-off     
OL,10,Fpayments in regions where there is high
OL,11,Fdemand for labour, with extra pay for  
OL,12,Fthose willing to work nights.          
OL,14,FFears over worker shortages have       
OL,15,Falready prompted other firms to warn of
OL,16,Fproblems in the run up to Christmas.   
OL,18,FAmazon began offering a #1,000         
OL,19,Fsigning-on bonus to recruit permanent  
OL,20,Fstaff in some regions in August.       
